summary: An ordinance authorizing and directing the Board of Public Works to purchase on government lots 6, 7 and 8, and section 18 of the north half of section 26, north half, Southwest quarter, north half of Southeast quarter of the Southwest quarter of the Southeast quarter of section 28; east half of the east half of section 30, township 22 north, range 9 east, W.M., and providing the method of paying the cost and acquiring the same.
